snippet.textDisplay:
Hello Asalamualaikum @cokestudio pakistan
Umeed krta hu ke is season main aap bhot saray masterpiece release kro. 
Jo ke abhi tak mujhe esa lagta hai ke koi ni hai 
I know ke aap thoda traditional and cultural songs prr zyada focus krr rhe ho , par you are meant to be the best. 
Aap apnay suparstar singers ko solo singing ka moka do like Ali sethi, Kavish, Atif aslam, shafqat anayat ali, abida parveen, Sajjad ali, Nabeel shaukat ali , shuja haider, momina mustehsen, Aima beigh, Quratulain baloch. aur bhe bhot saray. 
Jin singers ne cokestudiopakistan ka naam puri duniya main laya un ne last kuch seasons se bhot zyada songs ni diya
Hope ke aap ye mera mail padho 
Again like is baar Zeeshan ali sir ne bhe gaya par why are u making collabs. Han banavo agar aap ko acha lagta hai prr let these type of singers sing alone. 
And please release some classical songs like faasle, tera naam, maula tera noor, bewajah, sab jag soye, gulun main rang, rajish aur bhe bhot. 
And again hope you receive this msg and please if possible respond
Lots of love from India jammu and kashmir (kashmir)
